1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:31,899
=Episode 26=
(It is the longing that turns)

3
00:00:31,900 --> 00:00:33,379
(the mortal world into hell, )

4
00:00:33,380 --> 00:00:38,590
(and that same longing tries
to make it paradise.)

5
00:00:46,700 --> 00:00:49,060
General Pei Xiao greets Your Highness!

6
00:00:52,140 --> 00:00:52,980
Where is she?

7
00:00:53,060 --> 00:00:54,620
Mother went out yesterday.

8
00:00:54,660 --> 00:00:55,540
Where did she go?

9
00:00:57,540 --> 00:00:58,619
I don't know.

10
00:00:58,620 --> 00:00:59,820
General Pei, look!

11
00:01:09,670 --> 00:01:11,899
(Qingxin Pavilion)

12
00:01:11,900 --> 00:01:12,660
Chengjiang!

13
00:01:13,220 --> 00:01:14,020
Chengjiang!

14
00:01:15,460 --> 00:01:17,019
Quick! Get a physician!

15
00:01:17,020 --> 00:01:17,860
Yes!

16
00:01:18,140 --> 00:01:20,260
Chengjiang, what happened to you?

17
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:24,180
Her Highness went out yesterday.

18
00:01:24,580 --> 00:01:26,140
She wouldn't let me follow.

19
00:01:26,220 --> 00:01:27,900
I was scared something might happen,

20
00:01:28,380 --> 00:01:29,740
so I followed her.

21
00:01:30,180 --> 00:01:31,420
I saw Her Highness...

22
00:01:32,180 --> 00:01:33,860
get taken away by Zhang Muzhi.

23
00:01:34,700 --> 00:01:36,180
They were right outside the city at...

24
00:01:36,820 --> 00:01:37,580
Chengjiang!

25
00:01:39,340 --> 00:01:40,900
Outside the city at...

26
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:43,140
Ten-Mile Pavilion.

27
00:01:43,460 --> 00:01:44,300
Chengjiang!

28
00:01:45,780 --> 00:01:46,740
Go, now.

29
00:01:47,900 --> 00:01:49,140
Go, now!

30
00:01:53,900 --> 00:01:55,179
(Qingxin Pavilion)
Let's go, Xiao!

31
00:01:55,180 --> 00:01:55,899
Hurry!

32
00:01:55,900 --> 00:01:57,460
We're going to save Mother!

33
00:01:58,140 --> 00:02:00,100
the flower slaves are still missing.

34
00:02:00,700 --> 00:02:02,899
Stay here and watch over your father.

35
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:04,300
Don't leave his side.

36
00:02:05,700 --> 00:02:06,580
No.

37
00:02:07,420 --> 00:02:09,859
Mother told me to stay with Father.

38
00:02:09,980 --> 00:02:11,619
You have to bring Mother back.

39
00:02:11,620 --> 00:02:13,100
Go!

40
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:29,580
So this is it.

41
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:36,300
I never even did anything great.

42
00:02:37,140 --> 00:02:38,100
Father,

43
00:02:39,180 --> 00:02:40,740
I brought shame on you.

44
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:43,580
I didn't even get married.

45
00:02:47,060 --> 00:02:48,940
You little brat!

46
00:02:49,060 --> 00:02:50,820
You can't die yet.

47
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:52,339
Her Highness is in danger.

48
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:54,100
Crawl back if you have to.

49
00:02:54,460 --> 00:02:56,220
You're a soldier of the Pei Army.

50
00:02:56,340 --> 00:02:57,500
Get up!

51
00:02:58,940 --> 00:02:59,980
Father,

52
00:03:00,780 --> 00:03:03,700
you're already dead.
Why are you still nagging me?

53
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:07,220
But, Father...

54
00:03:07,780 --> 00:03:09,380
I miss you.

55
00:03:12,740 --> 00:03:14,940
You've always had your eye
on this flask.

56
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:16,340
Here.

57
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,260
No...

58
00:03:22,500 --> 00:03:24,059
There's no wine in it.

59
00:03:24,060 --> 00:03:25,379
Silly boy,

60
00:03:25,380 --> 00:03:27,219
ever since your mother left,

61
00:03:27,220 --> 00:03:29,380
this flask's been empty.

62
00:03:29,740 --> 00:03:30,940
Now get up.

63
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:33,940
This is too far from Baihua Hall.

64
00:03:34,740 --> 00:03:36,820
I don't think I can make it back.

65
00:03:37,220 --> 00:03:38,700
I'm so sleepy.

66
00:03:38,940 --> 00:03:40,339
If you fall asleep now,

67
00:03:40,340 --> 00:03:42,099
Her Highness could die.

68
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:43,779
If anything happens to her,

69
00:03:43,780 --> 00:03:47,379
Ning State will be thrown into chaos.

70
00:03:47,380 --> 00:03:48,820
My son,

71
00:03:49,340 --> 00:03:50,900
you've known since you were little

72
00:03:51,620 --> 00:03:53,900
to repay your country first.

73
00:03:58,620 --> 00:03:59,660
Get up.

74
00:04:00,860 --> 00:04:03,100
First, repay your country...

75
00:04:06,780 --> 00:04:10,340
Then, bring honor to your family.

76
00:04:28,780 --> 00:04:30,500
A young man should

77
00:04:31,780 --> 00:04:33,060
have great ambition.

78
00:04:35,020 --> 00:04:36,820
He should ride a fine horse

79
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:39,100
and cross the open plains.

80
00:04:40,100 --> 00:04:42,380
When the red sun rises,

81
00:04:42,620 --> 00:04:45,100
he'll still stand shoulder
to shoulder with the sky!

82
00:04:56,620 --> 00:04:59,420
Father, I did it!

83
00:05:08,930 --> 00:05:12,040
(Flower Slave Nest)

84
00:05:21,740 --> 00:05:23,740
Just to be safe,

85
00:05:24,220 --> 00:05:26,299
I used all the power in this staff

86
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:27,860
to set up a barrier.

87
00:05:28,180 --> 00:05:30,060
Even if it can't stop Ye Zhao,

88
00:05:30,620 --> 00:05:33,300
it'll definitely stop
that little sword spirit.

89
00:05:34,340 --> 00:05:37,180
Go bring all your shadow guards here.

90
00:05:38,060 --> 00:05:41,380
In case Pei Xiao storms
in with the Pei army.

91
00:05:41,980 --> 00:05:42,980
Immortal,

92
00:05:43,540 --> 00:05:44,940
once this formation is complete,

93
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:48,060
do we really not need
divine flesh and blood

94
00:05:48,220 --> 00:05:50,300
to turn my people into flower slaves?

95
00:05:52,340 --> 00:05:54,100
When have I ever lied to you?

96
00:05:56,660 --> 00:05:57,540
I'll go now.

97
00:06:09,740 --> 00:06:11,100
My people,

98
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:13,180
it's been a hundred years!

99
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:16,660
We won't have to survive
on human blood anymore!

100
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:17,860
My people,

101
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:20,500
let's be human again!

102
00:06:21,100 --> 00:06:24,220
Become human again!

103
00:06:24,300 --> 00:06:25,940
Become human again!

104
00:06:47,620 --> 00:06:49,219
Baobao, what are you doing here?

105
00:06:49,220 --> 00:06:50,539
I still had a bad feeling.

106
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:51,740
Did you find Mother?

107
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:53,860
She's inside.

108
00:06:54,540 --> 00:06:56,820
- No time to waste. I'm going in first.
- I'm going with you!

109
00:07:05,620 --> 00:07:06,980
There's a barrier.

110
00:07:07,980 --> 00:07:10,059
You two, go bring in the cannon unit!

111
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:10,740
Yes, sir!

112
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:13,300
Let's see how long it can keep me out!

113
00:07:16,340 --> 00:07:17,060
Baobao!

114
00:07:18,740 --> 00:07:19,420
Baobao,

115
00:07:20,300 --> 00:07:21,180
are you okay?

116
00:07:22,420 --> 00:07:23,299
Again!

117
00:07:23,300 --> 00:07:24,180
Together!

118
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:25,979
Chief,

119
00:07:25,980 --> 00:07:27,859
that sword spirit and Pei Xiao found us!

120
00:07:27,860 --> 00:07:29,980
Pei Xiao has called in the cannons!

121
00:07:30,420 --> 00:07:32,380
With the seer's barrier here,

122
00:07:32,540 --> 00:07:33,740
what are you panicking for?

123
00:07:34,340 --> 00:07:36,540
Let Helian Shu deal with the cannons.

124
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:39,620
Let's focus

125
00:07:40,220 --> 00:07:41,740
and activate the formation!

126
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:03,540
Mother,

127
00:08:04,220 --> 00:08:05,299
hang in there!

128
00:08:05,300 --> 00:08:07,300
I'm coming to save you!

129
00:08:26,300 --> 00:08:27,660
Mother!

130
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:37,500
Fifteen, twenty, fifteen!

131
00:08:43,740 --> 00:08:44,779
This is great!

132
00:08:44,780 --> 00:08:47,180
I have both a mother and a father now!

133
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:48,899
I'm so happy.

134
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:50,299
Mother!

135
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:51,060
Baobao!

136
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:52,500
Mother...

137
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:57,740
Long time no see,

138
00:08:58,060 --> 00:08:59,060
General Pei.

139
00:09:04,340 --> 00:09:05,740
So it's you.

140
00:09:05,980 --> 00:09:08,380
The traitor of Ning State.

141
00:09:08,660 --> 00:09:10,740
Today's traitor

142
00:09:11,060 --> 00:09:13,379
is tomorrow's emperor.

143
00:09:13,380 --> 00:09:15,060
Once I take Ning State,

144
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:18,180
I'll make you Grand General.

145
00:09:18,220 --> 00:09:19,900
You don't have the right!

146
00:09:20,220 --> 00:09:22,459
You just had to do this the hard way.

147
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:26,060
A sword spirit who can't
use magic on mortals

148
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:29,700
and a general with no troops at all.

149
00:09:33,340 --> 00:09:35,060
Can you really stop me?

150
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:37,700
If you want to die,

151
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:40,140
go ahead and try!

152
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:45,339
Mother...

153
00:09:45,340 --> 00:09:46,580
A divine heart

154
00:09:47,260 --> 00:09:48,820
can only be fixed by a divine heart.

155
00:09:49,460 --> 00:09:50,420
A divine heart...

156
00:09:50,460 --> 00:09:51,460
We need a divine heart!

157
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:52,939
A divine heart!

158
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:54,180
We need a divine heart!

159
00:10:02,980 --> 00:10:04,340
(Xiao...)

160
00:10:23,940 --> 00:10:26,379
Demigod, you really don't
care if you live or die.

161
00:10:26,380 --> 00:10:28,459
Fine. I'll use the hairpin as the tether

162
00:10:28,460 --> 00:10:29,859
to keep you alive.

163
00:10:29,860 --> 00:10:30,540
Baobao!

164
00:10:40,740 --> 00:10:41,940
This hair ribbon is for you.

165
00:10:42,100 --> 00:10:44,579
If you want to cry, cry.
If you want to laugh, laugh.

166
00:10:44,580 --> 00:10:47,180
Who cares about keeping up appearances?
Give me a smile.

167
00:11:08,740 --> 00:11:09,700
It worked!

168
00:11:12,940 --> 00:11:15,140
Everyone, it worked!

169
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:24,440
Why are those red eyes still here?
And the Red Spider Lily is still here too!

170
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,219
Why?

171
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:28,219
- Why didn't the formation work?
- Chief, what went wrong?

172
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:30,300
Seer, why is this happening?

173
00:11:32,340 --> 00:11:33,499
Finally!

174
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:35,940
I finally have a body of my own!

175
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:37,820
Cutie,

176
00:11:38,340 --> 00:11:39,820
for these two lifetimes,

177
00:11:40,380 --> 00:11:42,459
all I've ever wanted

178
00:11:42,460 --> 00:11:44,300
was your body.

179
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:48,060
Now lose yourself in the sweet dream

180
00:11:48,340 --> 00:11:49,780
I spun for you.

181
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:58,540
I did everything I promised you!

182
00:11:59,260 --> 00:12:02,140
What about the mortal joy
and pleasure you promised me?

183
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,900
Pleasure?

184
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:15,500
I

185
00:12:16,580 --> 00:12:18,620
am your pleasure.

186
00:12:21,540 --> 00:12:24,579
Thank you, my dear chief.

187
00:12:24,580 --> 00:12:27,780
If you hadn't rallied
the whole clan to help me,

188
00:12:27,940 --> 00:12:30,660
how could I have seen daylight again?

189
00:12:36,460 --> 00:12:37,220
Who...

190
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:39,020
Who are you?

191
00:12:49,900 --> 00:12:52,220
I'm your seer.

192
00:12:53,700 --> 00:12:55,660
How did you like

193
00:12:56,180 --> 00:12:58,300
that half demon heart of mine?

194
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:12,620
You lied to me for over a hundred years!

195
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:18,900
Who can blame me? You mortals
are so easy to fool.

196
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:23,220
If it weren't for the greed
in your hearts,

197
00:13:23,820 --> 00:13:26,140
how could I have pulled it off?

198
00:13:26,820 --> 00:13:28,500
Once your illness was cured,

199
00:13:28,940 --> 00:13:31,020
you started craving immortality.

200
00:13:31,580 --> 00:13:35,780
And after gaining immortality,
you still wanted paradise.

201
00:13:38,060 --> 00:13:39,419
How could anything that perfect

202
00:13:39,420 --> 00:13:41,500
exist in this world?

203
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:44,260
Kill her!

204
00:14:02,700 --> 00:14:03,780
Still fighting?

205
00:14:04,300 --> 00:14:06,100
You're the only one left!

206
00:14:06,180 --> 00:14:07,420
Who says

207
00:14:07,820 --> 00:14:09,780
he's the only one left?

208
00:14:19,620 --> 00:14:21,329
♪Even if reluctant, what can be done♪

209
00:14:21,330 --> 00:14:24,179
♪Chasing something always out of reach♪

210
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:26,919
♪So I'm afraid of goodbye♪

211
00:14:26,920 --> 00:14:28,549
♪Living the same day
over and over again♪

212
00:14:28,550 --> 00:14:34,150
(Perhaps, if I reincarnate,)

213
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,799
(I can rid myself of this demon heart.)

214
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:38,559
(I will definitely
come back to find you.)

215
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:41,409
(You must wait for me.)

216
00:14:41,410 --> 00:14:44,009
♪If in a dream♪

217
00:14:44,010 --> 00:14:48,799
♪I can hear your voice♪

218
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:50,559
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

219
00:14:50,560 --> 00:14:53,210
♪Let it be us♪

220
00:14:53,430 --> 00:14:56,149
♪drawing endlessly close♪

221
00:14:56,150 --> 00:14:57,799
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

222
00:14:57,800 --> 00:15:03,459
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

223
00:15:03,460 --> 00:15:04,999
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

224
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,749
♪Not even in time♪

225
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:10,719
♪to tell you how I feel♪

226
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:13,269
♪If the rain won't stop♪

227
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:17,909
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

228
00:15:17,910 --> 00:15:20,519
♪Let love go on♪

229
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:27,630
♪Until forever♪
